description: I have been creating generative art since 2010 using proprietary algorithms. This piece is one of the many directions I have discovered. — This “Digital Stitch” is the result of a large number of boundaries being woven. Incidentally, this is something I arrived at during my work on the theme of “worms that can hear music”. So this is the inside of an earthworm. ...Have you ever seen a dancing worm? - Qubibi ( more info bit.ly/3cvGyI4 ) 4700x3322px png
